ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
SubjectPIZZITELLI, The Hon. Frank J., RELOCATION EXPENSES additional
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. FRANK J. PIZZITELLI, who was required to relocate to Ottawa, Ontario, following his appointment as a Judge of the Tax Court of Canada on June 19, 2009.
